{"tid":928473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發][冇圖] 港獨黃教師 黑絲腿張開 淫招吸學生 一人一句譴責黃教師！","createTime":"2018-12-05T00:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T02:17:25.000Z","uid":4880,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"49f8219bb587e88b7682975b028af3fe5d0760bd","tid":928473,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:48:28.000Z","msg":"九十後港獨黃教師好唔檢點，勾引學生！黃絲港獨女性廢青補習學校開張，正當你以為佢哋修心養性做正行生意，誰不知轉頭竟然在FB開Live，穿著黑絲對住鏡頭示範「腿張開」、「絲襪好易爛」、無病呻吟「冇褲著」，一班血氣方剛嘅青年睇完之後再去上堂到底會點？呢間補習學校係咪掛羊頭賣狗肉？一人一句，譴責誨淫誨盜黃教師！<br />\n<br />\n幫港自講<br />\n<br />\n支持「港獨」、開口埋口藉「身體自主」為由去賣裸照嘅中大學生會前幹事黃于喬（Emilia Wong、圓咕碌），與另一名成日露肉「教師」搣時潘（潘書韻）一齊開補習社。<br />\n<br />\n黃于喬同搣時潘喺直播嘅時候就講到佢哋會開「成人英文班」同埋「高中英文班」，與此同時黃于喬就唔知點解講到自己被稱為「黑絲女神」，因為佢成日着黑絲，但出晒名鍾意賣裸照嘅妠N話，成日着黑絲係因為「冇錢買褲」。<br />\n<br />\n搣時潘聽緊黃于喬話自己係「黑絲女神」時都不甘示弱，即時張開雙腳，大show自己着咗條爛咗嘅黑絲，個叉開到上大髀內側。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲港獨女性廢青開補習學校，正當你以為佢哋修心養性做正行生意，誰不知轉頭竟然在FB開Live，穿著黑絲對住鏡頭示範「腿張開」、「絲襪好易爛」、「冇褲著」，一班血氣方剛嘅青年睇完之後再去上堂到底會點？呢間補習學校係咪掛羊頭賣狗肉？一人一句，譴責誨淫誨盜黃教師！<br />\n<br />\n原圖﹕<br />\n搣時潘FB<br />\nEMILIA WONG FB<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://silentmajority.hk/articles/98840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsilentmajority.hk%2Farticles%2F98840&d=1sVcEiuYA9%2FCtHdq16%2FHB7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8cd356a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://silentmajority.hk/articles/98840</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n重諗住打返個早晨丁，屌佢老母一開見唔撚到高清大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得個死人logo同張細到屌佢老母嘅相就當交左貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇圖學乜撚野人做傳媒？死返去作故仔算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d91a17cdd751e2f91b9e7f19c6aed915caf915d","tid":928473,"uid":172844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:49:49.000Z","msg":"都係要倒數嫁喇<br />\n10"},{"pid":"7118aeb6cbdf09e811dcb481b489e3459119f39c","tid":928473,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:50:34.000Z","msg":"幫党出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba15b6327d89561c3ac4aff8affa8fa7e5c3143","tid":928473,"uid":187076,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4bj6yu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4bj6yu.jpg&h=af3f81d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"750cdd4c1351b0fd746ebd277224064a4a80449b","tid":928473,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"晨早流流，要人屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1d52a7a7fcdb3392bdd0c36b832b82e0604463","tid":928473,"uid":11313,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rDyrzq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rDyrzq.gif&h=3f8acbc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c102df7ea7a2237a6622483c5605606d4d48a943","tid":928473,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:01:57.000Z","msg":"我要杜如風"},{"pid":"d3ea389345852c7911dd6b9011b9ad1c71030650","tid":928473,"uid":123914,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T01:17:25.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 正一死肥西<br />\nJ佢呢隻人形豬我留返督精暖肚好過<br />\n人又串 又肥 樣又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係得連登仔先咁雜 乜嘢狗屎垃圾都食"},{"pid":"e1850f0ca3a73bf331d0860032723bad71e9eafe","tid":928473,"uid":34223,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>冇人想睇依隻豬閪呀 貼圖死全家</strong></span></span>"}]}